    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced courgette</strong>, <strong>chopped spring onion</strong>, your <strong>ginger & garlic paste </strong>and your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)<strong> </strong>to the chicken and cook for 2-4 min or until fragrant</p>",
