    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>cornflour</strong> and 1 tsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>in a small bowl with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong>,<strong> </strong>then stir in your <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>gochujang paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) – this is your <strong>gochujang sauce</strong></p>",
